{
  "text": "Additionally, we analyzed the data with the software InStruct [CITATION_1] ) which, similarly to STRUCTURE, is a Bayesian clustering method but for inbreeding species. We tested K values from 2 to 20 with the same parameters as used for STRUCTURE, except that only seven iterations were done for each K.",
